cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper involves generating talking face landmarks from speech using a deep learning approach. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves processing visual information. The paper also involves speech processing, which falls under the category of signal processing (cs.SD). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it deals with speech recognition and generation. The paper also involves machine learning (cs.LG) as it uses a long short-term memory (LSTM) network for training. Finally, the paper involves multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with generating visual content from audio input.
